fields.value: China City Walls of Hebei and Shandong

dsDescriptionValue.value: The 1904-07 Prussian maps show the footprints of settlements including the outlines of city walls.  Small areas around each capital in the ChinaW file were clipped from the georeferenced maps.  Filenames contain the ChinaW ID number for each city.
